  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into thin fries</p><p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray with a small drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong>, give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until crispy</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
