      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken strips</strong>, <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>smoked paprika</strong> to a bowl, give everything a good mix up then set aside</p><p>Add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a plate with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> and mix everything together – this is your <strong>breadcrumb mixture</strong></p>",
